Documentation.name: CBA GDW 2.0
Documentation.notes: A set of custom elemnts, connectors and toolboxes to streamline GDW 2.0 design activities.

Tag.name: AS::command
Tag.description: Specifies the command, executable, UNIX shell script, application, or batch file to run.

Tag.name: AS::failed_codes
Tag.description: Defines which exit codes indicate job failure. By default any exit code other than 0 (zero) indicates job failure

Tag.name: AS::success_codes
Tag.description: Defines which exit codes indicate job success. Default: 0

Tag.name: TCF::Number of Threads
Tag.description: Number of threads system will use to executed TCF processes

Tag.name: TCF::Pattern
Tag.description: TCF Apply pattern used for TCF processes executed by the job

Tag.name: TCF::Process Names
Tag.description: Comma separated list of TCF process name patterns the job uses to determine list of TCF processes to execute. The patterns are specified using SQL wildcard symbols.

Tag.name: AS::success_codes
Tag.description: Comma separated list of exit codes treated as success

Stereotype.name: Poll Job
Stereotype.notes: The job will keep polling TCF/Mainframe Process completion by querying TCF Metadata/UTIL_UPI_ISAC table.

Tag.name: AS::Polling Offset
Tag.description: Business Date offset (+/-). Default value is 0

Tag.name: AS::Polling Stream ID
Tag.description: Specify coma separated list of TCF Stream keys or MVS job names

Tag.name: AS::Polling Table List
Tag.description: Comma separated list of tables

Tag.name: AS::Polling Interval
Tag.description: Time interval in minutes between attempts

Tag.name: TD::User Name
Tag.description: Teradata user name

Tag.name: AS::Polling Retries
Tag.description: Number of attempts

Tag.name: AS::Polling Exit Code
Tag.description: Exit code job returns when it exceeds number of attempts (default 1)

Tag.name: AS::success_codes
Tag.description: Comma separated list of exit codes treated as success
